lead_paragraph: Jon Lester was surprised when manager Joe Maddon let him bat in the eighth inning. After the pitcher struck out swinging, the rest of the night went according to plan.

headline.print_headline: Lester Goes Distance, Pitches Cubs Past Dodgers 2-1
